OvO Dimension for Chrome Extension is an exciting online game that can be played for free on the website https://classroom-6x.org/.
OvO Dimension is an engaging arcade platform game developed by Dedra Games. Players take control of a simple stickman character and must navigate through various levels using basic actions like jumping, wall jumping, and sliding. To master the game, players can experiment with action combinations, such as jumping after a slide or ground pound, to gain extra power and momentum. With an abundance of levels to conquer, players are challenged to jump their way through the OvO Dimension and see if they can complete all the stages.
